name: Far delivery food
description:
This game was made for the "WeeklyGameJam 172" with the theme "Catapult".

Far delivery food is a game in which player will have to throw fruits to people reclaiming them. You will have to reach the score in each level to continue playing.

Controls:

Take fruit -> Mouse click.
Launch fruit -> SpaceBar.

Assets made by Sheila <Izzy> Hernández
IG: https://www.instagram.com/_shvart/
